OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe Central Belt and south will
OL,6,Fbe dry with some sunny spells,
OL,7,Fclouding over this afternoon. Dry
OL,8,Facross Argyll this morning before
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain spread south this
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain across Argyll this
OL,13,Fevening will spread across the south
OL,14,Ffor a time overnight. Then dry weather
OL,15,Fwith clearing skies following on
OL,16,Fbehind. Cold with patchy frost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,19,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,20,Fsome sunny intervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
